Disclaimer:

This software is designed to interact with various social media platforms through their official APIs. Users are responsible for:

1. Obtaining proper API credentials and tokens
2. Complying with each platform's Terms of Service
3. Respecting rate limits and usage policies
4. Ensuring content posted meets platform guidelines
5. Protecting API credentials and sensitive information

The authors and contributors of this software:
• Are not responsible for misuse of the software
• Do not endorse any specific content or posting practices
• Are not liable for any violations of platform terms
• Recommend using the software responsibly and ethically

