Security Notice:

If you discover security vulnerabilities, please report them responsibly:
• Do not open public issues for security problems
• Email security concerns to: security@your-domain.com
• Allow reasonable time for fixes before public disclosure

---

Privacy Notice:

This software:
• Does not collect or store personal data beyond what you configure
• Stores API tokens locally or in your chosen database
• Does not send data to third parties except the social media platforms you configure
• Logs activities for debugging purposes only

Users are responsible for:
• Securing their API credentials
• Complying with privacy regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)
• Informing followers about automated posting if required
• Managing data retention according to their needs
